text:
Meet Acornia!

Acornia is one of the main coders on Amethyst, usually helping UOP along with a coding project or doing some of her own! She is responsible for the hackmons format available to play on Amethyst. She has also recently stepped up and become the official artist of Amethyst.

Tldr; The super creative, super active, super helpful user of Amethyst.

Acorn is the main nickname but also gets hl'd as Sticks anf Acorn-Chan.
